<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="153" type="remarks">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="153">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="153">The Simian Mountain Nature Reserve is located in the southwest of Chongqing Municipality. The region has a subtropical humid monsoon climate with abundant rainfall, and the vegetation types are mainly tropical and subtropical coniferous and broad-leaved mixed forests.</paragraph>
